                <!-- /wp:heading -->
                
                <!-- wp:paragraph -->
                <p class="paid">All accounts, including but not limited to; free, lifetime, trial, and or paid accounts, etc are subject to a disk storage size and or usage of servers bandwidth, data transmission limits, etc as provided in their accounts. Subscriber must pre-pay in advance for additional fee, as provided in their agreement or the current price structure when the subscriber is about to exceed their limits on data storage and or its transmission limits beyond about 80% of their limit size or minimum two work days before the end of its limits. To enjoy uninterrupted Service, the subscriber must have prepaid, or have provided for advanced billing options, and this billing must materialize promptly.<br>
                If no such arrangements have been made, the Service may be interrupted until such time that the additional charges are paid. The account shall be deemed closed and the data shall be deleted that are unpaid accounts for this reason, beyond 5 days of the interruption of Service.</p>
